{"tid":1070483,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"身邊既人睇得起你都唔係件好事","createTime":"2019-03-20T16:23:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T12:05:52.000Z","uid":230645,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"67bf458a1992a732ba56b9fc43d2f53ed3b64ed2","tid":1070483,"uid":230645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T16:23:04.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n<br />\n老細同上司睇得起，加我工作量，人工就係咁易加左<br />\n<br />\n同事，朋友睇得起，話我唔應該繼續留係而家既公司，值得有更好既發展。最後我都接受意見辭左，當然因爲本身自己心思思想走，咁岩有人支持下就確定走。<br />\n<br />\n黎緊反新工，我係一個好易緊張好易有壓力既人。其實都幾驚適應新公司，因為文化同而家仲做緊個份完全唔同，要重新黎過，好驚融入唔到，又唔知係咪真係好發展。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b32544e546e5f26cd65ce30de546bfd70fd92ad","tid":1070483,"uid":230645,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T16:24:03.000Z","msg":"屋企人又覺得轉新工應該係好發展，自己覺得無形壓力多左"},{"pid":"9bc572407ee2aaffcd8f0de929af078c58699522","tid":1070483,"uid":60393,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T16:28:10.000Z","msg":"唔好介意我咁講 客套說話黎嘅姐"},{"pid":"29a71928ce46b3eae446aa03ea7500d1dff8de88","tid":1070483,"uid":63311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T16:29:00.000Z","msg":"反你老母"},{"pid":"eaa7d6cc365e0c095cec4762cc58babb569e0294","tid":1070483,"uid":127905,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T16:31:03.000Z","msg":"其實做人簡單d就得 係咪多左人工？"},{"pid":"eceac9079b0f0660ca9c84e37bb850a9fa377653","tid":1070483,"uid":23225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T16:39:47.000Z","msg":"我寧願睇得起我加人工升職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f94fb2a2fe5161911b183078b46e3917e0fdd817","tid":1070483,"uid":75692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T16:52:34.000Z","msg":"做野為錢姐<br />\n邊度錢多咪做邊度囉"},{"pid":"77ca834016e95631c49cf4a6a2d1df5e8cc515f6","tid":1070483,"uid":135689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9bc572407ee2aaffcd8f0de929af078c58699522","tid":10